<Head title="Title II & VII Policy" description="View our Title II & VII Policy to understand your rights!" author="Alex Toucan" />
<div id="page">
  <Navbar />
  <main id="titleiivii" class="container">
    <h1 class="title"> Title II & VII Policy </h1>
    <h5> Last Updated: <time>April 2nd, 2023</time>. </h5>
    <h5> Into Effect: <time>April 3rd, 2023</time>. </h5>
    <p class="my-3">
      <i>Our only current active volunteering service is the <a href="https://beta-testing.atproducts.xyz">Department of Beta Testing</a>. No current employment opportunities is being offered.</i>
    </p>
    <p class="my-3">
      <i>All of these titles refer to the <a href="https://www.archives.gov/milestone-documents/civil-rights-act">Civil Rights Act of 1964</a>. </i>
    </p>
    <h3>Title II Policy</h3>
    <p> It is the policy of AT Products LLC that all customers, partners, etc. shall not be discriminated against due to sex, race, color, national origin, religion, or handicap and that no customer or any other person will be subject to discrimination.</p>
    <h3>Title VII Policy</h3>
    <p> It is the policy of AT Products LLC that all employment and volunteering opportunities will be offered without regard to sex, race, color, national origin, religion, or handicap and that no employee or any other person will be subject to discrimination. We will accommodate religious practices dependent on employees and volunteers.</p>
  </main>
  <Footer />
  <BackToTop />
